    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but my doctor is always so dismissive when i bring up natural stuff and i really dont want to wait weeks for an appointment just to be told no. i've heard from people in my support group that they made the switch just fine and felt way better. if i just taper off the sertraline over a few days and then start the st johns wort, isn't that a safe way to do it? i just want to avoid the chemical side effects.",
