    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i know you have to say that but im really struggling right now and i feel like i know my body better than some doctor who has 10 mins with me. if i just do a very slow taper—like cutting the dose in half for a week then quarters—and then start a standard dose of the supplement, what's the actual science behind the risk? is it really that dangerous to just replace a synthetic chemical with a plant-based one if the mechanism is the same?",
